title: 187: Inside OTAs, NBA/NFL player comparisons
itunes:title: 187: Inside OTAs, NBA/NFL player comparisons
description:
Matt “Money” Smith fills in for a vacationing Daniel Jeremiah to discuss the ins and outs of organized team activities with Bucky Brooks. The guys also get ready for the NBA Finals by comparing Warriors and Cavs stars to NFL players and building a competitive starting five consisting of current football standouts.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
